Hello Tom,

Not sure I fully understand what you&#39;re trying to accomplish. Do you 
want to follow all links? In that case, change the initial 
RejectDecideRule in your scope to an AcceptDecideRule. Do you want to 
crawl links one hop off from the initial sites? Then you may want to try 
alsoCheckVia. Or are you trying to do something more complicated, like 
dns lookups for all offsite links, even if the links themselves are not 
crawled? In that case you might need to write a custom extractor and 
perhaps custom scope rules as well.

Noah

